metadata.name: #1 OHYUNA
metadata.description: Oh Yuna PFP( Picture For Profile ) project is the Genesis in the AV world, Ogura Yuna in the real world, will become OhYuna and aiming for doing a lot of activities in the Metaverse and Web 3.0 space, starting from Korea and Japan and it will be eventually spread out globally.  After the release of OhYUNA NFT, Marketplace, Tokenomics and Album presentations are planned for this project, and it will also work as an avatar in the metaverse world.
